  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a medium pot over medium heat.",
    "Add smoked paprika, rosemary, nutmeg, and garlic; sauté for 1 minute.",
    "Add diced tomatoes, white beans, vegetable broth, and bay leaf; bring to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low, add salt and pepper; cook for 15 minutes until beans are tender.",
    "Broil for 5 minutes to create a flaky, golden crust on top.",
    "Remove from heat, let rest for 2 minutes before serving."
